episodes.synopsis: Brandeis wants a job and gets offers from Leela and Chris, but he can’t fold laundry or sweep with his paws.

video.title: Animals & Nature
video.synopsis: Kids will laugh and learn about animals and nature when Elmo and his Sesame Street pals meet fireflies, baby birds and even a dog that wants a job!
